  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink70-kilavi">parattaiyarōṭu poḻutupōkki neṭitu tuyttuvanta talaimakaṉōṭu
          talaimakaḷpulantu colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink70">
          <l>paḻaṉap paṉmī ṉarunta nārai</l>
          <l>kaḻaṉi marutiṉ ceṉṉic cēkku</l>
          <l>mānīrp poykai yāṇa rūra</l>
          <l>tūyar naṟiyarniṉ peṇṭir</l>
          <l>pēe yaṉaiyamiyāñ cēypayan taṉamē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg xml:lang="en">

          <l> O man from a fertile village with ponds of great water!</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> Where the crane, after eating many fish in the tank,</l>
          <l rend="indent4"> rests on the top of the Myrobalan tree by the paddy field – </l>
          <l> Pure [and] fragrant are your women.</l>
          <l> [But] we are like demonesses: we have born your child.</l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
